<h4>Input Sizes and Placeholders</h4>

<p>This module provides four size qualifiers: <code>.mini</code>, <code>.small</code>, <code>.large</code> and <code>.full</code>. The sizes of the first three are configurable via SASS variables, whereas the <code>.full</code> class signifies that the input should be full width. This module also provides support for coloring the <code>placeholder</code> attribute.</p>

<pre class="prettyprint">&lt;form class="form"&gt;
    &lt;div class="control"&gt;
        &lt;label for="i-6-1"&gt;Mini&lt;/label&gt;
        &lt;input id="i-6-1" class="mini"&gt;
    &lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;div class="control"&gt;
        &lt;label for="i-6-2"&gt;Small&lt;/label&gt;
        &lt;input id="i-6-2" class="small"&gt;
    &lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;div class="control"&gt;
        &lt;label for="i-6-3"&gt;Default&lt;/label&gt;
        &lt;input id="i-6-3"&gt;
    &lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;div class="control"&gt;
        &lt;label for="i-6-4"&gt;Large&lt;/label&gt;
        &lt;input id="i-6-4" class="large"&gt;
    &lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;div class="control"&gt;
        &lt;label for="i-6-5"&gt;Full&lt;/label&gt;
        &lt;input id="i-6-5" class="full"&gt;
    &lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;div class="control"&gt;
        &lt;input type="submit" class="button"&gt;
    &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/form&gt;</pre>

<form class="form">
    <div class="control">
        <label for="i-6-1">Mini</label>
        <input type="text" id="i-6-1" class="mini">
    </div>
    <div class="control">
        <label for="i-6-2">Small</label>
        <input type="text" id="i-6-2" class="small">
    </div>
    <div class="control">
        <label for="i-6-3">Default with Placeholder</label>
        <input type="text" id="i-6-3" placeholder="placeholder">
    </div>
    <div class="control">
        <label for="i-6-4">Large</label>
        <input type="text" id="i-6-4" class="large">
    </div>
    <div class="control">
        <label for="i-6-5">Full</label>
        <input type="text" id="i-6-5" class="full">
    </div>
    <div class="control">
        <input type="submit" class="button">
    </div>
</form>

<p>These size classes and the <code>placeholder</code> attribute may be used on <code>input</code> (except for <code>checkbox</code> and <code>radio</code>) and <code>textarea</code> elements.</p>

